{"tid":130649,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【一代宗師】最年輕諾貝爾經濟學獎得主辭世 享年95歲","createTime":"2017-02-22T14:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T22:23:43.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7165b970a940e51e672280af6329e86e8d68e87f","tid":130649,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/215835_de48e1c2bcaee125866e845681a267a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F215835_de48e1c2bcaee125866e845681a267a9.jpg&h=c899b056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n史上最年輕的諾貝爾經濟學獎得主Kenneth J. Arrow離世，享年95歲。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1i61aS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1i61aS.jpg&h=4d22ec2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKenneth J. Arrow（左）於2006年獲（右）美國前總統喬治布殊，頒授美國國家科學獎章。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/220006_2d4a115c603d1b51aac51736c72e060b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F220006_2d4a115c603d1b51aac51736c72e060b.jpg&h=70091425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位經濟學殿堂級大師曾於史丹福大學任教。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57R5pw3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57R5pw3.jpg&h=e07529a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKenneth J. Arrow領取諾貝爾經濟學獎的一刻。(美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n經濟學殿堂級大師、史上最年輕的諾貝爾經濟學獎得主肯尼斯&middot;阿羅（Kenneth J. Arrow）於本港時間今日下午在加州帕羅奧圖的家中離世，享年95歲。<br />\n<br />\n肯尼斯・阿羅在一般均衡理論及社會福利經濟的研究，於1972年獲得肯定，當年與英國經濟學家Sir John R. Hicks共同奪得諾貝爾經濟學獎。他獲獎時為51歲，成為諾貝爾經濟學獎最年輕的得獎者，其紀錄保持至今。<br />\n<br />\n肯尼斯&middot;阿羅先後於美國著名學府任教，包括史丹福大學及哈佛大學。他於1980年退休後，一直從事研究工作，被視為二戰後新古典主義經濟學的代表人物。<br />\n<br />\n出身於「經濟學世家」的肯尼斯&middot;阿羅，其姪子是美國前財長薩默斯，小叔則是已故美國經濟學大師Paul A. Samuelson。據《紐約時報》報道，Paul A. Samuelson稱讚經濟學殿堂級大師是「20世紀最重要的經濟學家」，他的研究對經濟學、投資產品、金融證券及僱傭合約等影響俱深。肯尼斯&middot;阿羅學術成就橫跨經濟領域，他在奪取諾貝爾經濟學獎前，曾提出社會選擇理論（Social choice theory）證明投票選舉缺陷。<br />\n<br />\n這位經濟學殿堂級大師桃李滿門，當中包括四位諾貝爾經濟學獎得主：John Harsanyi、A. Michael SpenceEric Maskin和Roger Myerson。2001年獲得諾貝爾經濟學獎得主的斯蒂格利茨（Joseph Stiglitz）也視他為啟蒙大師。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56340607&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56340607%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170222&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8529Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=76c04d82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56340607%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170222&h=674df3cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56340607&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170222</a><br />\n<br />\n//係其他人作品介紹過佢嘅 Social choice theory"},{"pid":"f76b6b6ecba8aef1f4d36602e568cd5d19813f9d","tid":130649,"uid":62881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n曾幾何時幻想過係學術發展<br />\n<br />\n可惜係香港只能夠向現實低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b15428a489b4c932340c34df67b4f2931c7128","tid":130649,"uid":1009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"初代補習名師<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f27802bf12bb4dd6eb85517257b77f505281d0","tid":130649,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:14:13.000Z","msg":"張五常介紹過Arrow嘅Social choice theory，冇記錯佢譯做「難能定律」，簡單講一個選舉入面有A,B,C三個候選人，選民十名，結果A得四票，B,C各得三票，A當選，但係社會最優選擇唔係最好，有6票並唔認同"},{"pid":"d2d3566751906b10a1187da3068ec0ca09d8879f","tid":130649,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張五常介紹過Arrow嘅Social choice theory，冇記錯佢譯做「難能定律」，簡單講一個選舉入面有A,B,C三個候選人，選民十名，結果A得四票，B,C各得三票，A當選，但係社會最優選擇唔係最好，有6票並唔認同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVicF 師兄好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d5715ba07defb769f4b5176ec09ec6d486bbf2","tid":130649,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arrow's_impossibility_theorem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FArrow%27s_impossibility_theorem&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8529Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=6a665c55\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arrow's_impossibility_theorem</a><br />\n原來就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641e78215ef847623efad7213d4b86f132d2d4f6","tid":130649,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T22:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>張五常介紹過Arrow嘅Social choice theory，冇記錯佢譯做「難能定律」，簡單講一個選舉入面有A,B,C三個候選人，選民十名，結果A得四票，B,C各得三票，A當選，但係社會最優選擇唔係最好，有6票並唔認同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVicF 師兄好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  冇睇過佢任何著作，只係睇過「知識二道販子」嘅介紹，經濟學呢類嘢對炒股/投資冇用㗎，Irving Fisher都係經濟學一代宗師，輸到甩轆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}